Package org.fosstrak.llrp.commander.util

Class Summary
LLRP This class can be used to get information on the LLRP protocol.
LLRPArrayConstraint This class represents an LLRP constraint stating that a certain array field must not be empty.
LLRPConstraints This class states additional LLRP constraints which are not modeled in llrp-1x0-def.xml.
LLRPFactory This class lets you generate default LLRP messages automatically.
LLRPPresenceConstraint This class represents an LLRP constraint stating that a certain parameter is mandatory.
LLRPRangeConstraint This class represents an LLRP range constraint.
LLRPTreeMaintainer This class constitutes the interface to llrp message objects.
MessageBoxRefresh helper thread that periodically refreshes the message box view if a new message has arrived.
Range This class represents a numeric range.
Utility helper class that holds utility routines.
